videos.description: Mason Jones lobs an alley-oop dunk to Adrio Bailey, which sends the Arkansas crowd into a frenzy.

videos.description: J'Von McCormick dishes to Isaac Okoro who lays it in the bucket, propelling Auburn to the 79-76 overtime victory over Arkansas.
